strings.Value: "Do you really not like to have fun â€“ or you just don't know how to? Do you want me to hold a festival for you when we get back to the capital? We can stuff our faces, dance, and get drunk! What do you say?"
"I say you are very kind, Octavia, but such help will do me no good. I'll only get a headache from the music and dancing. As for the drinking... Hm, hm... Well, I better keep away from that too."
